{
  "verses": [
    {
      "n": 1,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "A KUNGA Wahrd̄s notikke us Jonasu A mitajus Dehlu/ kas ẜazzija:"
    },
    {
      "n": 2,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Zellees/ eij uhs Niniwi to leelu Bilstahtu / un fluddina prett winnu/ jo winna Blehdiba irr uhskahputi manna Preekfcha."
    },
    {
      "n": 3,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Bet Jonas zehlahs/ ka tas behgtu uhs Tarsu no ta KUNGGA Preekfchas/ un wiꞥſch nonahze uhs Jahwu/ un atradde tur weenu Laiwu / kas uhs Tarsu zehlahs/ un eedewe winnas Maksu/ un kahpe eekfcha/ un gribbeja ar teem uhs Tarsu zeltees no ta KUNGA Waiga."
    },
    {
      "n": 4,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Bet tas KUNGS likfe nonejautchu weenu leelu Wehju nahkt Juhra/ un tappe leela Wehtra Juhra/ ta ka ta Laiwa likkabs puſcham etjoti."
    },
    {
      "n": 5,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Tad bthjajahs tee Laiwineeki/ un kleedse ikweens uhs Jawu Deewu / un mette tohe Rihkus/ kas Laiwā bija/ Juhra/ to patchu no teem atweegli naht. Bet Jonas bija nogahjis Laiwās Dibvinā/ un gulleja"
    },
    {
      "n": 6,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Tad nahze pee winna tahē Laiwas Wirfneeks/ un ẜazzija us winnu : Ka tu tik zeeti gulli? Zellees/ peesauz taru Deewu/ jafchu Deews muhs peeminnehs/ ka mehs bohja ne eetam."
    },
    {
      "n": 7,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Pehz ẜazzija tee weens uhs ohtru: Nahzeet / meslofimees/ ka mehs atsibstam/ kurra dehtschis Lannums mums useet? Un tee meslojahs/ tad tappe Jonas eesibmehts."
    },
    {
      "n": 8,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Tad ẜazzija tee uhs winnu: Stahsti mums jelle/ kadeht tchis Lannums par mums nahk? kas irr taws Darbs? un no kurrenes tu nahzi? Kurra irr tawa Seinme? un no kurraä Tantas effi tu?"
    },
    {
      "n": 9,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Tad ẜazzija wiꞥſch uhs teem: Es esmu weens Ebreeris/ un bihstoos to KUNGU to Deewu no Debbes/ kas Juhru un Sauunu irr darrijs."
    },
    {
      "n": 10,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Tad bthjajahs tee Wiḣri ar leelu Bihjaschanu/ un ẜazzija uhs winnu : Ka effi tu scho darrijs? Jo tee Wiḣri finnaja/ ka wiꞥſch no ta KUNGA Waiga behdse/ jo wiꞥſch bija teem to stahstijs."
    },
    {
      "n": 11,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Un tee ẜazzija uhs winnu : Ko darrifim mehs ar tew/ ka ta Juhra mums nostahjahs? jo ta Juhra tappe jo ilgaki jo breefmigakt."
    },
    {
      "n": 12,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Un wiꞥſch ẜazzija uhs teem: Pazelleet manni/ un metteet mannt Juhra/ tad ta Juhra jums nostahjees/ jo es finna/ Eze"
    }
  ],
  "confidence": "high",
  "notes": ""
}
